API?
-> API(application programming interface) is a definition of method which two programs conversation.
If rules about giving and taking data between A and B, we can't process data correctly.

HTTP?
-> HTTP(hyper text transfer protocol) is basic communication method convey web page from internet

If we make API using HTTP protocol, it called web orient API

HTML?
-> HTML(hypertext markup language) is a kind of document which web browser show on screen and standard language for web page